<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="no"><head><title>Forskrift om hva som i avgiftsmessig forstand omfattes av begrepet kraftkrevende industri.</title><base href="https://lovdata.no/" /></head><body><header class="documentHeader" id="hode"><dl class="data-document-key-info"><dt class="xmlGenerated">XML generert</dt><dd class="xmlGenerated">2025-11-18 09:18:24</dd><dt class="legacyID">Datokode</dt><dd class="legacyID">FOR-1986-09-25-1865</dd><dt class="dokid">DokumentID</dt><dd class="dokid">LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865</dd><dt class="ministry">Departement</dt><dd class="ministry"><ul><li>Finans- og tolldepartementet</li></ul></dd><dt class="publishedIn">Publisert i</dt><dd class="publishedIn">Avd I 1986 Nr. 20</dd><dt class="dateInForce">I kraft fra</dt><dd class="dateInForce">1986-09-25</dd><dt class="appliesTo">Gjelder for</dt><dd class="appliesTo">Norge</dd><dt class="dateOfPublication">Kunngjort</dt><dd class="dateOfPublication">1986-10-15</dd><dt class="title">Tittel</dt><dd class="title">Forskrift om hva som i avgiftsmessig forstand omfattes av begrepet kraftkrevende industri.</dd><dt class="refid">RefID</dt><dd class="refid">forskrift/1986-09-25-1865</dd><dt class="table-of-contents">Innhold</dt><dd class="table-of-contents"><ul class="tocTopUl"><li>Forskrift om hva som i avgiftsmessig forstand omfattes av begrepet kraftkrevende industri.<ul class="tocSubUl"><li>§ 1.</li><li>§ 2.</li><li>§ 3.</li><li>§ 4.</li><li>§ 5.</li><li>§ 6.</li></ul></li></ul></dd></dl></header><main class="documentBody" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865" id="dokument"><h1>Forskrift om hva som i avgiftsmessig forstand omfattes av begrepet kraftkrevende industri.</h1><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/1/" id="ledd-1">Finansdepartementet har 25. september 1986 i medhold av Stortingets vedtak av 17. juni 1986 om avgift på elektrisk kraft § 1, tredje ledd fastsatt følgende forskrift:</article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865/§1" data-name="§1" data-partID="§1" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/" id="paragraf-1"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 1</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-1-ledd-1">Denne forskrift gjelder virksomhet som etter § 1, annet ledd i Stortingets vedtak av 17. juni 1986 skal være unntatt fra økning av avgift på elektrisk kraft som kraftkrevende industri og treforedlingsindustri.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865/§2" data-name="§2" data-partID="§2" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/" id="paragraf-2"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 2</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1">Følgende industrigrupper (Statistisk Sentralbyrås næringsgrupper) skal regnes som kraftkrevende industri:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">1.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Jern- og stålindustrien (næringsgruppe 37101)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">2.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Ferrolegeringsindustrien (næringsgruppe 37102)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">3.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Aluminiumsindustrien (næringsgruppe (37201)</article></article></li></ul></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2">I tillegg regnes følgende virksomheter som kraftkrevende industri:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">1.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-1-ledd-1">Norsk Hydro A/S, Porsgrunn Fabrikker (magnesiumproduksjonen)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/2/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">2.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1">Falconbridge Nikkelverk, Aktieselskap</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/3/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">3.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1">Norzink A/S, (Zinkverket)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="4." data-name="4."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/4/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">4.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-1">Vigeland Metal Refinery A/S</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="5." data-name="5."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/5/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">5.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1">Arendal Smelteverk A/S</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="6." data-name="6."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/6/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-6"><span class="data-originalId">6.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/6/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-6-ledd-1">Norton A/s</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="7." data-name="7."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/7/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-7"><span class="data-originalId">7.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/7/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-7-ledd-1">Odda Smelteverk A/S</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="8." data-name="8."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/8/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-8"><span class="data-originalId">8.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1">Orkla EXolon A/s &amp; co.</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="9." data-name="9."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/9/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-9"><span class="data-originalId">9.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/9/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-9-ledd-1">Norsk Hydro A/S, Rjukan Fabrikker</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="10." data-name="10."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/10/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-10"><span class="data-originalId">10.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/10/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-10-ledd-1">Norsk Hydro A/S, Glomfjord Fabrikker (amoniakkproduksjonen)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="11." data-name="11."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/11/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-11"><span class="data-originalId">11.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/2/ledd/2/punkt/11/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-2-ledd-2-punkt-11-ledd-1">Sameiet Alkali</article></article></li></ul></article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865/§3" data-name="§3" data-partID="§3" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/3/" id="paragraf-3"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 3</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/3/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-3-ledd-1">Som treforedlingsindustri forstås næringsgruppene 34111 – 34115.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865/§4" data-name="§4" data-partID="§4" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/4/" id="paragraf-4"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 4</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/4/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-4-ledd-1">Der kraftprisen er avtalt inkludert avgift ("1976-kontrakter") kan den enkelte bedrift etter søknad til Toll- og avgiftsdirektoratet få refundert den for meget betalte avgift.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865/§5" data-name="§5" data-partID="§5" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/5/" id="paragraf-5"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 5</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/5/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1">Nærmere bestemmelser om gjennomføringen av denne forskrift gis av Toll- og avgiftsdirektoratet.</article></article><article class="legalArticle" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1986-09-25-1865/§6" data-name="§6" data-partID="§6" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/6/" id="paragraf-6"><h2 class="legalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">§ 6</span>.</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/paragraf/6/ledd/1/" id="paragraf-6-ledd-1">Denne forskrift trer i kraft straks og gjøres gjeldende for kraft levert i annet halvår 1986.</article></article></main></body></html>